---
/* small grid of feature cards used in the page */
---
<section id="features" class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Better, together.</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Analytics To Help Your Business Grow Stronger Everyday.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold">Dashboarding</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Dash By Plotly and PowerBI allow for beautiful data visualizations that show which areas your business can improve management.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold">Data Warehousing</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Put your Data in a Supabase powered managed PostgreSQL instance to keep track of many sources and indicators in one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold">LLM Powered Data Insights</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Chat with your data and understand the mathematical and statistical inferences that allow for improved business decisions. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold">A Better Tomorrow</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Improving strengths and weaknesses will make your business more efficient and reach more people.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
